{
  "stem": "20686.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we live-- my father was a-- we were trying to sell whatever we could, you know, whatever we had that were in our possessions.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We saved constantly.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father made it-- with that money, we established a cleaning business.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they cleaned things from, from other people who could, could afford more money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was not life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was-- that's the way it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the first stages, it was no communal life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But later on, we reorganized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We regrouped later on as the ghetto was established.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think I just told you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I just mentioned it to you that the-- it, it-- everything went so swift that the-- all these harassments which I spoke about and, and this sort of constant infringement on our-- on our freedom, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] this was part of a plan.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The establishment of the ghetto, the establishment-- a hierarchy of, of Jews who will be able to cooperate with the Germans, this is of one-- you know, one of the most important aspect of the Holocaust, as far as the Germans were concerned, is to annihilate the Jews in secrecy and orderly.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The victim are not supposed to know till the last moment that he is going to annihilated.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And order has to be.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And for that, they, they found their stooges hidden amongst our people, like-- I mean, like Chaim Rumkowski, who collaborated with them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] One cannot-- it would be false to accuse to say that he knew exactly, in, in, in the initial stages what is taking place when we are taking from ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But later on, he knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he still collaborated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he thought that he's going to outsmarten them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was stupid.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
